{"tid":2326221,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的 今日食左餐免費早餐","createTime":"2020-12-15T07:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T07:41:47.000Z","uid":79793,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8915776126c4ff6cd563532acca1c9193c713972","tid":2326221,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:23:27.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"pink\">今日起身凍到尻縮唔想落街買早餐<br />\n屋企又冇哂材料煮野食<br />\n我就叫我女朋友就即刻Down番個heymandi <br />\n個主題係「好凍呀唔想落街買早餐❤」<br />\n我用女朋友部手機用十分鐘嘅時間同三個男仔交換左tg<br />\n之後我女朋友錄音同佢地三個人講左句「如果有人可以買外賣比我就好啦」<br />\n佢地三個都好巧合咁問我住邊，我就如實答左佢啦<br />\n有兩個話好遠，搵日出黎食飯，我即刻block柒左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">其中一個就講：「好遠啊買唔到比你，不如我叫外賣比你」</span><br />\n我就同佢講左想食咩，地址就填左我樓下個公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉屌，原來香港地做女人真係大撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"c6fd205b6b85c49f97a2d209a8fe3dc876a0c418","tid":2326221,"uid":202520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:30:34.000Z","msg":"噉食咗咩？"},{"pid":"f5925d129d488c7c6e0c43bf802a8a82dcdcaeed","tid":2326221,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:31:10.000Z","msg":"小妹唔係啲咁既人，你溝我啦"},{"pid":"fa88ca95e04094b32264b9cc80bee57a17ce3bd5","tid":2326221,"uid":263223,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:32:17.000Z","msg":"咁咪又係凍到鳩縮都要落樓下公園拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb29c890647973b80dbeacfe5c6ed3ae149347a0","tid":2326221,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c6fd205b6b85c49f97a2d209a8fe3dc876a0c418","tid":2326221,"uid":202520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:30:34.0